originalText.text: I can honestly say, I am so proud of these group of individuals. Growing up with Garifuna parents in the United States, we never had the opportunity to be vocal about our Heritage, we are very proud people. The Garifuna Market is a new outlet for this generation and generation to come. Every day, every week and every month, they share videos, of Garifuna people and it make me proud. Having the opportunity to have a market, that we from Central America can purchase Accessories on-line is awesome. We never had a place to purchase anything before, Garifuna Market honestly is the first on-line business I have every seen. I pray for bigger and greater things for them.

originalText.text:
TheGarifunaMarket has definitely been the answer to my prayers. A blessing to the Garifuna culture. My name is Tatiana and I am Garifuna and a true fan of TheGarifunaMarket E-commerce.
TheGarifunaMarket brings style and class while keeping the authenticity of our roots. I consider TheGarifunaMarket the bridge to keeping Garifuna people connected throughout the globe. I support their mission on unity and expression of our roots. TheGarifunaMarket is also the medium to educating our younger blossoming generation and other cultures on what it is to be Garifuna.

Their products are amazing and sent out timely. I love the packaging; you can feel the passion and love they put in just sending your order. It is very important that we find ways to keep the culture together and they definitely nailed it.

I am a proud Garifuna and thank you to TheGarifunaMarket for the stylish ways I can show it.

Keep up the amazing work.

Love

Tatiana

originalText.text: Being a child of a Honduran immigrant, discovering The Garifuna Market has become a breath of fresh air for individuals such as myself. It has allowed me regain a sense of pride & spark of interest in reconnecting with a community that has always played a part of my upbringing while growing up in the Bronx as an Afro Latino. It brings a great deal of joy to know that founder Siria Alvarez is at the forefront in preserving & bringing awareness to the culture for the next generation to embrace.
